1452
01:22:03,119 --> 01:22:05,185
from USAID.

1453
01:22:05,187 --> 01:22:08,555
We now have a submission
from Mrs. Mary Morgan

1454
01:22:08,557 --> 01:22:10,958
from South Hall,
