were magnificent.

1541
01:27:45,327 --> 01:27:46,526
No, no, no, no.

1542
01:27:46,528 --> 01:27:51,365
I mean I'm--
I'm sorry I
took George away.

1543
01:27:51,367 --> 01:27:54,901
I never said
I'm sorry.

1544
01:27:54,903 --> 01:27:57,971
And I'm sorry
you weren't in
the little school,

1545
01:27:57,973 --> 01:28:00,240
and I'm sorry
you weren't
on the beach,

1546
01:28:00,242 --> 01:28:02,042
and I'm glad
you weren't
in the hospital

1547
01:28:02,044 --> 01:28:05,779
holding his hand,

1548
01:28:05,781 --> 01:28:12,853
but I am so sorry
I never said sorry.

1549
01:28:12,855 --> 01:28:15,455
It's OK.

1550
01:28:15,457 --> 01:28:16,456
It's OK now.

1551
01:28:16,458 --> 01:28:18,325
Yeah?
Yeah.

1552
01:28:18,327 --> 01:28:25,532
♪

